{"tid":98941,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解有人鍾意爭埋單  ???","createTime":"2017-01-28T19:13:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T19:22:54.000Z","uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b44b328c8aef843e9c8782dc204629b87e808a00","tid":98941,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T19:13:05.000Z","msg":"70 幾年前已經有人批評過呢樣野 on9 <br />\n<br />\n當在搶付車費，搶會鈔，或搶買戲票的時候，為了面子關係，不好意思不「搶」，為了荷包關係，卻又不最堅持要「搶」，結果是得收手且收手，面子顧全了，荷包仍舊不空。最糟糕的是遇 了同道的人，你一搶他就放鬆，結果雖然是「求仁得仁」，卻變了啞子吃黃連，心裏有說不出的苦。 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YANU12.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYANU12.gif&h=021113e0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YANU12.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYANU12.gif&h=021113e0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YANU12.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYANU12.gif&h=021113e0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n《請客》王力<br />\n原載於一九四三年十月出版的《生活導報》"},{"pid":"11f4e608fc8c7f9735afd101d401776b74c7a7eb","tid":98941,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T19:13:51.000Z","msg":"《請客》王力<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fed.cuhk.edu.hk/f4f5chin/chin16/text.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fed.cuhk.edu.hk%2Ff4f5chin%2Fchin16%2Ftext.htm&d=7FZwGubSg%2Boc5%2FIyI3je95kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=a460f077\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fed.cuhk.edu.hk/f4f5chin/chin16/text.htm</a>"},{"pid":"759c396a6098706c4e42653e817c9cb4436d86f4","tid":98941,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T19:20:06.000Z","msg":"因為力王埋你單"},{"pid":"7dfc6b5ab2c6389244855e8a709be5601c39ccf4","tid":98941,"uid":17618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T19:22:16.000Z","msg":"以前可能為左面子<br />\n但依家其實唔想欠人"},{"pid":"595ff1ebd790085a9fe52557df15c588c0eee20f","tid":98941,"uid":20625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy